reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 11, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Buy These - You Won't Be Sorry
reviews.reviewText: I have been using a cube type of packing system for over 20 years. I don't even pack for an overnight trip without using them. Most of the ones I have had were the standard square ones and they have worked great. I had to start traveling more for business last year and decided to give these a try. I can honestly say that these are the best one's I have ever had.Before the pandemic hit, I traveled with these at least five times. It did not matter if I used a carry-on rolled suitcase or a checked one, these fit inside the case perfectly. The various sizes make it easy to pack what you need. Jeans and button down shirts go in the large size. Rolled t-shirts go in the medium size. Socks and underwear go in the small. Non-clothing items can go in whatever size works best for what you have to pack. I never travel without a power strip, adapter and cable for my phone and other various cables. The medium size case is perfect for this.The biggest feature is that they do not waste any space. By having the rounded corners, they fit right to the corners of the bag without any gaps. That is what makes these stand out like they do. The quality is also very good. Zippers all move with ease and I believe these will last for years to come.These bags will change the way you pack.I hope you find this review helpful. If you do, please click Yes. That helps anyone who takes time to review an item know if it was worth the time.
